<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= state.name %> Income Tax Calculator | MyTaxCalcs</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Use our free <%= state.name %> income tax calculator to estimate federal taxes and state tax information.">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
<script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="small-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">MyTaxCalcs</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="container two-column">
    <section class="card">
      <h1><%= state.name %> Income Tax Calculator</h1>

      <% if (state.hasIncomeTax) { %>
        <p>Estimate your federal tax while detailed <%= state.name %> state tax formulas are added.</p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p><%= state.name %> does not have a broad-based state income tax. Use this page to estimate your federal income tax.</p>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/<%= state.slug %>-income-tax-calculator" class="form">
        <label>
          Gross annual income
          <input type="number" name="grossIncome" value="<%= form.grossIncome || '' %>" placeholder="85000" required>
        </label>

        <label>
          Filing status
          <select name="filingStatus">
            <option value="single">Single</option>
            <option value="marriedJoint">Married Filing Jointly</option>
            <option value="marriedSeparate">Married Filing Separately</option>
            <option value="headHousehold">Head of Household</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label>
          Deduction type
          <select name="deductionType">
            <option value="standard">Standard deduction</option>
            <option value="itemized">Itemized deduction</option>
          </select>
        </label>

        <label>
          Itemized deduction amount
          <input type="number" name="itemizedDeduction" value="<%= form.itemizedDeduction || '' %>" placeholder="0">
        </label>

        <label>
          Federal tax withheld
          <input type="number" name="federalWithheld" value="<%= form.federalWithheld || '' %>" placeholder="12000">
        </label>

        <label>
          Tax credits
          <input type="number" name="taxCredits" value="<%= form.taxCredits || '' %>" placeholder="0">
        </label>

        <button type="submit">Calculate Estimate</button>
      </form>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Estimated Results</h2>

      <% if (!result) { %>
        <p class="muted">Enter your information to see your estimate.</p>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="results">
          <p><span>Taxable income:</span> <strong>$<%= Math.round(result.taxableIncome).toLocaleString() %></strong></p>
          <p><span>Federal tax after credits:</span> <strong>$<%= Math.round(result.federalTaxAfterCredits).toLocaleString() %></strong></p>

          <% if (state.hasIncomeTax) { %>
            <p><span><%= state.name %> state tax:</span> <strong>Coming soon</strong></p>
          <% } else { %>
            <p><span><%= state.name %> state income tax:</span> <strong>$0</strong></p>
          <% } %>

          <% if (result.refundOrOwed >= 0) { %>
            <p><span>Estimated federal refund:</span> <strong>$<%= Math.round(result.refundOrOwed).toLocaleString() %></strong></p>
          <% } else { %>
            <p><span>Estimated federal amount owed:</span> <strong>$<%= Math.abs(Math.round(result.refundOrOwed)).toLocaleString() %></strong></p>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <p class="disclaimer">Estimate only. Not tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <section class="container content seo-content">
  <p class="eyebrow dark"><%= state.name %> Tax Calculator Guide</p>
  <h2>About this <%= state.name %> income tax calculator</h2>

  <% if (state.hasIncomeTax) { %>
    <p>
      This <%= state.name %> income tax calculator page helps users estimate federal income tax
      while reviewing state-specific tax information. State income tax rules can vary by filing
      status, deductions, credits, taxable income, and local rules, so the state estimate should
      be treated as a planning estimate only.
    </p>
  <% } else { %>
    <p>
      <%= state.name %> does not have a broad-based state income tax. This page focuses on
      estimating federal income tax while showing that the state income tax estimate is $0
      for broad-based state income tax purposes.
    </p>
  <% } %>

  <div class="seo-grid">
    <div class="seo-mini-card">
      <h3>Federal estimate</h3>
      <p>
        The calculator estimates federal taxable income, federal tax after credits,
        refund or amount owed, and related federal tax details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="seo-mini-card">
      <h3><%= state.name %> tax note</h3>
      <% if (state.hasIncomeTax) { %>
        <p>
          <%= state.name %> has state-specific income tax rules that may require additional
          deductions, exemptions, credits, or state tax tables.
        </p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>
          <%= state.name %> does not have a broad-based state income tax, but residents may
          still pay other taxes such as sales tax, property tax, or local taxes.
        </p>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="seo-mini-card">
      <h3>Estimate only</h3>
      <p>
        Results are for educational planning only and should not be used as tax, legal,
        accounting, or financial advice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2><%= state.name %> income tax FAQ</h2>

  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Does <%= state.name %> have state income tax?</h3>
      <% if (state.hasIncomeTax) { %>
        <p>
          Yes. <%= state.name %> has state income tax rules that may apply to residents
          and some nonresidents. The final amount can depend on income, filing status,
          deductions, credits, and state-specific rules.
        </p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>
          <%= state.name %> does not have a broad-based state income tax. However, residents
          may still owe federal income tax and may pay other types of state or local taxes.
        </p>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Does this calculator include all <%= state.name %> tax rules?</h3>
      <p>
        No. This calculator is designed for simple estimates. It may not include every
        state deduction, credit, exemption, local tax rule, or special tax situation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Why does my refund or amount owed change?</h3>
      <p>
        Your estimate changes when income, filing status, deductions, withholding, or credits
        change. Withholding is especially important because it affects whether the calculator
        shows a refund or an amount owed.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I use this for tax filing?</h3>
      <p>
        No. This page is for planning and educational estimates only. For filing, use official
        tax forms, tax software, or a qualified tax professional.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What should I check after using this calculator?</h3>
      <p>
        Review your filing status, income, withholding, credits, deductions, and any state-specific
        tax rules that may apply to your situation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
</section>

  <section class="container content">
    <h2>All State Calculators</h2>
    <div class="state-list">
      <% states.forEach(function(item) { %>
        <a href="/<%= item.slug %>-income-tax-calculator"><%= item.name %></a>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
    <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    <p>© 2026 MyTaxCalcs.com</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

